<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Jonathan Johnson.">
  <article class="wrap article">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        I am a defensive specialist and security researcher focused on Windows internals, telemetry, and AI security.
        I research adversarial tradecraft to find ways to identify, expose, and prevent it - approaching offensive
        techniques through a defender's lens. This blog is where I write up that research, walking through the
        thought process and methodology behind each finding rather than just the result.
      </p>
      <p>
        Find me on <a href="https://github.com/jonny-jhnson">GitHub</a> · <a href="https://x.com/JonnyJohnson_">X</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
